<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1437,1589,2010]" pageId="14" pageNumber="115">Head and thorax greenish yellow, crown of vertex with irregular light brown to dark brown spots. Face and pronotum mottled with dark brown. Median spot on forewings not so distinct.</paragraph>
